<html>
<body>

<p>
Hello, $assignment.giftGiver.nickname!
<p>

<p>
This email was auto-generated by the
<a href="http://santa-exchange.appspot.com">Santa Exchange</a>
program on behalf of the organizer, $exchange.organizer.name.
If you need to, you may contact the organizer:
</p>

<table>
    <tbody>
#if( "$!exchange.organizer.phoneNumber" != "" )
        <tr>
            <td><b>Phone:</b></td>
            <td>$exchange.organizer.phoneNumber</td>
        </tr>
#end
#if( "$!exchange.organizer.emailAddress" != "" )
        <tr>
            <td><b>Email:</b></td>
            <td>$exchange.organizer.emailAddress</td>
        </tr>
#end
    </tbody>
</table>

<p>
Below is your assignment for the "$exchange.name"
Secret Santa exchange.  No one else knows what your
assignment is.  You should keep your assignment a secret.
</p>

<table>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Your "Secret Santa" buddy is:</b></td>
            <td>$assignment.giftReceiver.name</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>The theme of this exchange is:</b></td>
            <td>$exchange.theme</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>The exchange will take place on:</b></td>
            <td>$exchange.dateAndTime</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>The suggested cost of your gift is:</b></td>
            <td>$exchange.cost</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

#if( "$!exchange.extraInfo" != "" )
<p>
The organizer has also provided this additional information:
</p>

<blockquote>
<p>
$exchange.extraInfo
</p>
</blockquote>
#end

</body>
</html>
